194	Monitor AI Model Inputs	As an AI compliance officer,\nI want to monitor AI model inputs for sensitive personal data,\nSo that I can prevent the ingestion of non-compliant training data.	4	@monitorAiModelInputs @Gdpr @Compliance @DataPrivacy @DataMonitoring @DataSecurity\nFeature: Monitor AI Model Inputs\n  As an AI compliance officer,\n  I want to monitor AI model inputs for sensitive personal data,\n  So that I can prevent the ingestion of non-compliant training data.\n\nBackground:\n  Given I have appropriate access to the system\n\nScenario: Validate user consent for AI model inputs\n  When I receive new data for the AI model\n  And I check for user consent\n  Then I should confirm that consent is valid and documented\n\nScenario: Handle data deletion requests\n  When a data deletion request is received\n  And the data is identified within the AI model inputs\n  Then I should ensure the data is removed and logged appropriately\n\nScenario: Log access to AI model inputs\n  When an access request is made to view AI model inputs\n  And the request is approved\n  Then I should log the access with user details and timestamp\n\nScenario: Ensure compliance with cross-border data restrictions\n  When AI model inputs are sourced from different regions\n  And cross-border data restrictions are applicable\n  Then I should verify compliance and document the legal justification	2025-07-28 00:01:53.960809	f	t	\N	\N	backlog	2025-08-26 02:52:52.92033	generic	draft	{}	{"overallComplexity":7,"scenarios":[{"name":"Validate user consent for AI model inputs","complexity":5,"factors":{"stepCount":3,"dataDependencies":4,"conditionalLogic":2,"technicalDifficulty":3},"explanation":"Moderate complexity due to the need to validate and document user consent, which involves data verification and compliance checks."},{"name":"Handle data deletion requests","complexity":6,"factors":{"stepCount":3,"dataDependencies":5,"conditionalLogic":3,"technicalDifficulty":4},"explanation":"Complexity a